column1: 1939 Census has observer at White House Guildford Rd Sheet has no distances or elevation as received late
1949 Newspaper lists him at Fernhurst Kings Rd House not found but NGR likely and matches distances and elevation
1940 Did he move in 1940 Guildford Rd is about third of a mile SE Elevation about 250ft
1955 Observer is 87 and recovering from a stroke No queries or letters should be sent re errors on returns
